;Add these sections to the parent list of your weapon sections to have them inherit scope setup without needing to rewrite or remember the different variables every time ;you setup a scope. You will still need to setup variables for one off scopes but this will cover the majority of scopes in GAMMA/Anomaly. Below is an example section of ;what a clean scope section setup should look like under this system. These sections do not store use_alt_aim_hud or laser_status. Section names reflect the scope they go ;to. _magd_off sections should be treated as red dots and should not inherit the scope info.
;
;[wpn_adar2_15_marchf]:wpn_adar2_15, marchf_s
;hud				= wpn_adar2_15_marchf_hud
;visual				= dynamics\weapons\wpn_adar2_15\wpn_adar2_15_world.ogf
;
;1icon_layer                              = marchf
;1icon_layer_x                            = 75
;1icon_layer_y                            = -8
;
;[wpn_adar2_15_marchf_hud]:wpn_adar2_15_hud
;item_visual		= dynamics\weapons\wpn_adar2_15\wpn_adar2_15_marchf_hud.ogf
;

